Package iahmadgad.json

Class JSONArray

java.lang.Object
iahmadgad.json.JSONArray
public class JSONArray extends Object
JSONArray Class.

JSONArray is an array contains an ordered sequence of values, values can only be integers, doubles, booleans, or nested JSONObjects & JSONArrays, but it can't be chars or any other type.

Since:
0.3
Version:
